    "faq_QwmYQP": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question_AmL8wb": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "ABOUT LIFETIME REPLACEMENTS OF SMARTWATCHES AND OTHER PRODUCTS:",
            "answer": "<p>When you join Carbinox EPC, any Carbinox smartwatch you own will be fully covered against scratches, dents, broken screens, and more. To apply for a replacement, simply contact your VIP representative. We’ll provide you with a pre-paid return label to ship your product back to us, and we’ll send you a new one at no cost.</p><p><em><strong>Please note: We only approve replacements for smartwatches purchased after August 1st, 2023. It is mandatory to ship your old smartwatch to our facility to receive a new unit.</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_qdbqxA": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "ABOUT LIFETIME FREE ACCESSORIES FOR YOUR SMARTWATCH:",
            "answer": "<p>As a member, you will gain instant access to free tempered glasses, USB chargers, and original bands for your smartwatch. You will be provided with a URL where you can order what you need AT NO COST. We only charge $5 to cover shipping, pick and pack, materials, and handling by our employees.</p><p>Please note:</p><ul><li>You can include up to one (1) accessory per order.</li><li>You can place up to three (3) orders per month.</li><li>We only ship the original band that comes with your smartwatch.</li></ul><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_bxFzzx": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "ABOUT MYSTERY GIFT EVERY 90 DAYS:",
            "answer": "<p>Only for our members, we'll be shipping you new products every 90 days at no cost. These products could be special gadgets, limited edition bands, and more.</p><p>You won't have to do anything to claim your gifts, they'll be shipped automatically.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_XVr7My": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "ABOUT PRIVATE FACEBOOK GROUP:",
            "answer": "<p>As soon as you become a member, you will receive an email or text message with a custom URL to join our Facebook group. Simply request access, and we'll review your information and approve your membership promptly.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_rNm3KK": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "ABOUT LIFETIME 25% OFF:",
            "answer": "<p>You will receive a custom discount code linked to your email address. To enjoy your 25% off every time you order, please use the same email address you used to purchase the membership.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_hAdQr6": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "ABOUT EARLY ACCESS TO NEW PRODUCTS:",
            "answer": "<p>Every time we launch a new product, you will be the first to find out. We will publish all the information weeks before the launch on the Facebook Private Group, giving you exclusive access and a special discounted price.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_eMqmnY": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "ABOUT CANCELLATIONS:",
            "answer": "<p>It would be really bad to see you go. However, if a cancellation is needed, just reach our VIP department at paulina@shopcarbinox.com and we'll help you out. <br/></p><p>*We do not provide any refunds if you were already charged for the membership.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
